6.  If the correct key and password (optional) are used on the file, a success message dialog box will appear.  
7.  In the **Notification Output Folder** field, the location of the decrypted and signed xml file that contains the contents of the notification are present. For example, the file name 000000.00000.TA.840_Payload.xml is used in this sample.  


